                "invention-title": [
                    "Nuclear energy heat supply and hydrogen production system coupling waste incineration power generation and anaerobic fermentation",
                    "一种耦合垃圾焚烧发电及厌氧发酵的核能供热制氢系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a nuclear energy heat supply and hydrogen production system coupling waste incineration power generation and anaerobic fermentation, which comprises a high-temperature gas cooled reactor, a waste classification treatment system and a high-temperature methane steam reforming hydrogen production system, redundant heat meeting the peak regulation requirement is stored in the fused salt heat storage unit and used for high-temperature methane steam reforming hydrogen production, and heat of condensate water is used for improving the working efficiency of the fermentation tank; the garbage classification treatment system is used for carrying out classification treatment on dry and wet garbage and then carrying out incineration power generation, methane preparation through fermentation and crude oil extraction, and a biogas outlet of the garbage classification treatment system is communicated with a biogas inlet of the high-temperature methane steam reforming hydrogen production system through a heat absorption side of the high-temperature gas cooled reactor. Meanwhile, electric energy, hydrogen and crude oil can be supplied to the outside, and garbage recycling and zero-carbon nuclear energy efficient hydrogen production are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种耦合垃圾焚烧发电及厌氧发酵的核能供热制氢系统，包括高温气冷堆、垃圾分类处理系统及高温甲烷蒸汽重整制氢系统，其中，高温气冷堆的二回路蒸汽主要部分用以驱动透平做功，适应调峰要求的多余热量储存到熔盐储热单元用于高温甲烷蒸汽重整制氢，冷凝水的热量用于提高发酵池工作效率；垃圾分类处理系统将干湿垃圾分类处理后用于焚烧发电、发酵制甲烷和提炼原油，垃圾分类处理系统的沼气出口经高温气冷堆的吸热侧与高温甲烷蒸汽重整制氢系统的沼气入口相连通，该系统能够实现核能制氢和垃圾处理，同时可以对外供给电能、氢气及原油，实现垃圾资源化和零碳核能高效制氢。"
                }
            ]
